; Regression test for issue #1789: unbalanced transaction when using `format`
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1789
; The commodity `format` directive should only affect output display, not balance
; checking precision. With `format 1000.00 B`, ledger rounds -0.001 B to 0.00 B
; during balance verification, causing a false "unbalanced transaction" error.
commodity B
    format 1000.00 B

2000/01/01 note
    Account    -0.001 B
    Account         1 A

test bal -> 1
__ERROR__
While parsing file "$FILE", line 11:
While balancing transaction from "$FILE", lines 9-11:
> 2000/01/01 note
>     Account    -0.001 B
>     Account         1 A
Unbalanced remainder is:
                 1 A
Amount to balance against:
                 1 A
Error: Transaction does not balance
end test
